(45, 143, 'フィード配信モジュール', 'フィード配信モジュール', '<p>配信モジュールはユーザがあなたのサイトから取得できるフィードリンクを表示することができます。フィード配信が可能なページのみに表示されます。つまりを単一記事、コンタクトまたはこのようなウェブリンクページには表示されないことを意味します。<a href="http://docs.joomla.org/Help15:Screen.modulessite.edit.15#Syndicate" title="フィード配信モジュール">ヘルプ</a></p>\r\n<div class="sample-module">{loadposition syndicate,Syndicate}</div>', '', 1, 67, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 1, 6, '', '', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(46, 144, 'システム', 'システム', '<p>システムプラグインはサイトのページが読み込まれるごとにで動作します。URL、ログインモジュールにユーザがログイン情報を記憶する（Remember me）ボックスにチェックできるかどうか、またキャッシュを有効にするかどうか、といったものを制御します。新機能はリダイレクトプラグインで、URLの変更の管理をアシストするリダイレクトコンポーネントです。</p>\r\n<p>標準で有効:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Remember me <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#System_-_Remember_Me">ヘルプ</a></li>\r\n<li>SEF <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#System_-_SEF">ヘルプ</a></li>\r\n<li>デバッグ <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#System_-_Debug">ヘルプ</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>標準で無効:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>キャッシュ <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#System_-_Cache">ヘルプ</a></li>\r\n<li>ログ <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#System_-_Log">ヘルプ</a></li>\r\n<li>リダイレクト <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#System_-_Redirect">ヘルプ</a></li>\r\n</ul>', '', 1, 25, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":